thread.title: Laura

author: Laura
title: Laura
text: Sarah is a great property manager who I really enjoy working with. She currently manages 2 properties for us and is the best agent we've worked with to date. She is honest, professional, responsive and prompt with queries. Sarah is proactive in ensuring the properties achieve the correct market value and reviews rental pricing regularly and inspects accordingly providing reporting on such matters.
